.col-md-4.col-xs-12
  .white-box
    .user-bg
      %img{:alt => "user", :src => "../plugins/images/large/img1.jpg", :width => "100%"}/
      .overlay-box
        .user-content
          %a{:href => "javascript:void(0)"}
            %img.thumb-lg.img-circle{:alt => "img", :src => "../plugins/images/users/genu.jpg"}/
          %h4.text-white User Name
          %h5.text-white info@myadmin.com
    .user-btm-box
      .col-md-4.col-sm-4.text-center
        %p.text-purple
          %i.ti-facebook
        %h1 258
      .col-md-4.col-sm-4.text-center
        %p.text-blue
          %i.ti-twitter
        %h1 125
      .col-md-4.col-sm-4.text-center
        %p.text-danger
          %i.ti-dribbble
        %h1 556
.col-md-8.col-xs-12
  .white-box
    %ul.nav.nav-tabs.tabs.customtab

      %li.tab
        %a{"aria-expanded" => "false", "data-toggle" => "tab", :href => "#profile"}
          %span.visible-xs
            %i.fa.fa-user
          %span.hidden-xs Profile

      %li.tab.active
        %a{"aria-expanded" => "true", "data-toggle" => "tab", :href => "#settings"}
          %span.visible-xs
            %i.fa.fa-cog
          %span.hidden-xs Settings
    .tab-content

      #profile.tab-pane
        .row
          .col-md-3.col-xs-6.b-r
            %strong Full Name
            %br/
            %p.text-muted Johnathan Deo
          .col-md-3.col-xs-6.b-r
            %strong Mobile
            %br/
            %p.text-muted (123) 456 7890
          .col-md-3.col-xs-6.b-r
            %strong Email
            %br/
            %p.text-muted johnathan@admin.com
          .col-md-3.col-xs-6
            %strong Location
            %br/
            %p.text-muted London
        %hr/
        %p.m-t-30 Donec pede justo, fringilla vel, aliquet nec, vulputate eget, arcu. In enim justo, rhoncus ut, imperdiet a, venenatis vitae, justo. Nullam dictum felis eu pede mollis pretium. Integer tincidunt.Cras dapibus. Vivamus elementum semper nisi. Aenean vulputate eleifend tellus. Aenean leo ligula, porttitor eu, consequat vitae, eleifend ac, enim.
